'''''Temple of Terror''''' is a video game published by [[Adventure Soft]] in 1987 for the [[Commodore 64]] and [[ZX Spectrum]].

==Gameplay==
''Temple of Terror'' is an adaptation of the ''[[Fighting Fantasy]]'' [[gamebook]], ''[[Temple of Terror]]''.

==Reception==
''[[Zzap!64]]'' reviewed the game, rating it 35% overall, and stated that "I have to admit that they show very little advance in design or content over, for example, ''The Hulk'' - or even some of the earlier titles like ''Adventureland''.  Come on boys, we're in the Infocom Age, not the Stone Age ..."<ref name="zzap">{{cite magazine|title=Chronicles of the White Wizard|magazine=[[Zzap!64]]|issue=28|date=August 1987|page=38}}</ref>

